<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="60" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,290,713]" pageId="9" pageNumber="60">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,614,641]" pageId="9" pageNumber="60">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Light reddish tan dorsally with head and pronotum darker; anterior clypeal margin emarginate medially; antennae composed of 10 antennomeres, antennomeres 8–10 lamellate; protibia distinctly tridentate; elytral disc with scattered setae.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
